      <div class="space-y-16">
        <section>
          <h1 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">
            About
          </h1>
          <article class="space-y-4">
            <p>
              Jie Li is a Postdoctoral Researcher in Computer Science at Texas Tech University, where he is a member of the <Link href="https://discl.cs.ttu.edu/doku.php?id=home">Data-Intensive Scalable Computing Laboratory (DISCL)</Link> under the guidance of <Link href="https://www.myweb.ttu.edu/yonchen/">Dr. Yong Chen</Link>. Jie completed his Master of Science degree in Computer Science from Texas Tech University in 2019. Prior to that, he earned a bachelorâ€™s degree in architecture.
            </p>
          </article>
        </section>

        <section>
