            Research Summary
          </h1>
          <article class="space-y-4">
            <p>
              My research journey in Computer Science has been deeply rooted in the realm of High-Performance Computing (HPC) with a multifaceted approach. My commitment lies in exploring innovative solutions for advancing HPC system management, operational data analytics, job scheduling, and system architecture. Leveraging a blend of academic expertise and practical experience, I have actively engaged in pioneering research endeavors that contribute to the advancement of HPC systems and their performance optimization.
            </p>
          </article>
